    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cyclops strenuus (Fischer, 1851) from China, Xinjuang, Tianchi Lake. Female. A, P 1. B, P 4. C, P 5. D, furcal ramus ventrally. E, pediger 5 and genital double-somite, ventral. F, basipodite of antenna, frontal side. G, palp of maxillula. Scale bar: A ̅ H = 100 µm." ;
